      <p begin="01:07:46,488" end="01:07:48,876">- [meyer] Otra cosa que necesitas<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>resaltar es...</p>
      <p begin="01:07:51,963" end="01:07:55,913">El llamado Escape.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>E-S-C-A-P-E.</p>
      <p begin="01:07:55,913" end="01:08:00,006">Te sugiero que te lleves<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>uno o dos a casa.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:00,006" end="01:08:00,901">- Ok.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:00,901" end="01:08:02,711">- Estos son frijoles</p>
      <p begin="01:08:02,711" end="01:08:06,039">Puedes ver como abrazan el palo.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:06,039" end="01:08:07,281">&#161;y ves esto?</p>
      <p begin="01:08:07,281" end="01:08:07,827">- Si</p>
      <p begin="01:08:07,827" end="01:08:10,740">Comienzan a nacer jitomates</p>
      <p begin="01:08:17,013" end="01:08:20,629">- &#191;te consideras optimista o<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>esc&#233;ptico sobre los seres humanos?</p>
