      <p begin="01:08:55,346" end="01:08:58,948">y reciclar las bolsas de pl&#225;stico.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:58,948" end="01:09:04,265">Mientras se sientan as&#237;, ning&#250;n<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>pol&#237;tico va a interesarse.</p>
