      <p begin="01:09:27,370" end="01:09:29,046">Michelle escribe para Businessweek</p>
      <p begin="01:09:29,046" end="01:09:30,018">-Si</p>
      <p begin="01:09:30,018" end="01:09:33,304">Diariamente se talan millones<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>de &#225;rboles</p>
