      <p begin="01:11:07,477" end="01:11:09,107">- No, no lo es</p>
      <p begin="01:11:09,107" end="01:11:10,894">-[Myriam] es como mierda...</p>
      <p begin="01:11:10,894" end="01:11:14,488">-Si, es mierda. Mierda de gusano</p>
